The ultimate summer routine ✨
@lydiamillen uses all Rodial to create a a bronzed summer glow without any powders. Products used:

✨ Bronze Glowlighter
✨ Banana Lowlighter 
✨ Blush Drops shade Frosted Pink
✨ Glass Paper

@nikki_makeup uses the New Bronze Glowlighter to add a natural warmth to the complexion, and to sculpt the high points of the face ✨
This cream bronzer hybrid can also be mixed with your moisturiser or foundation to add a golden glow ✨

Loving this gorgeous Rodial glow on the stunning @shaninamshaik ✨ Shanina uses the filling Rodial products for this effortless look:

Rodial VIT C Scrub 
Rodial VIT C Pads 
Rodial Banana Lowlighter
Rodial Glass Powder
Rodial Blush Drops Sunset Kiss & Frosted Pink 
Rodial XXL Waterproof Mascara

@thetennillelife_ uses the Bee Venom Cleansing Balm to brighten and plump the skin. 
Ingredients include Bee Venom, Vitamin C & Salicylic Acid that all work together to smooth fine lines and help reduce the appearance of pigmentation.
